{"tid":2349630,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"怎樣才算贏家謙？","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T03:42:52.000Z","uid":58512,"like":23,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c640880ad74a6e5c12ea785c94774bc0ef41304","tid":2349630,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:30:34.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算贏家謙？<br />\n<br />\n1.要在家謙狀態好的時候才頒獎<br />\n2.要在家謙作好大量歌曲才頒獎<br />\n3.你不能fans多過我<br />\n4.你不能令fans買太空卡鳩投票<br />\n5.你的歌曲要令家謙fans識80%才可拎獎，否則勝之不武<br />\n6.你不能贏唱作人金獎<br />\n7.你不能說家謙的不是(eg 唱功.....)<br />\n8.你的Youtube/Spotify view數不能高過家謙<br />\n9.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏獎了，家謙迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。家謙迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏獎。"},{"pid":"53f39081f6b887a8ae6c301e5d0e4f3f16e648da","tid":2349630,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a6da0007832e5dc66e64f16ec2c6a38509ef8a","tid":2349630,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55aa7a0cb07ec8b1a9355d3897f8faa0caad9b28","tid":2349630,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b8091e18af3093130edac4c588b2e5dec3eb3f","tid":2349630,"uid":364041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200316/5YUOHTH3JYYHLSUSQRLR2RMKKQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200316%2F5YUOHTH3JYYHLSUSQRLR2RMKKQ%2F&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=3f73f691\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=htt